snippet.title: RoboCop: Rogue City | Part Man, Part Machine trailer
snippet.description:
Only RoboCop can clean up the crime-ridden streets of Old Detroit!

Follow the part man, part machine in this gameplay trailer combining detective work and gory shoot-outs. Reinforcements arrive on November 2, 2024!
